{"tid":1697552,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Pixel 4 XL 一拗即斷   四點斷裂情況慘不忍睹","createTime":"2019-11-07T02:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T04:26:37.000Z","uid":109923,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"57a95f109874ee3ff566a435c9978296b9f7a92e","tid":1697552,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T02:28:58.000Z","msg":"自從 Google 以巨額收購 HTC 的精英開發團隊後，就沒有再將 Pixel 手機的設計外判予其他手機生產商，變相所有出現於 Pixel 手機的軟硬件問題，都是 Google 自己的責任，與其他廠商無關。早前上市的 Pixel 4 XL 日前現身於 YouTube，接受頻道 JerryRigEverything 的嚴苛測試，結果卻令人相當失望。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXiOLhm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXiOLhm.jpg&h=e008de0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPixel 4 系列上市至今約 3 星期，似乎 Google 無論是軟件還是硬件都有不足的地方，系統的整體表現和 90Hz 屏幕都屬於軟件層面，日後有望通過系統更新修正改善。不過 JerryRigEverything 的測試則顯示，Pixel 4 XL 的硬件和其他旗艦有一段距離，例如抗刮測試在 Level 6 就已經出現屏幕刮痕，到了 Level 7 更出現明顯刮花。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OoQ5Nwf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOoQ5Nwf.jpg&h=97c639ba&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n更嚴重的則是 Pixel 4 XL 一拗即斷的問題，JerryRigEverything 稍稍施加外力，手機就已經承受不了，是近期測試中最脆弱的手機。斷裂的位置多達 4 處，可以用慘不忍睹去形容。經過仔細觀察後發現，導致斷裂的原因跟天線設計有關，雖然 JerryRigEverything 嘗試為 Google 解釋開脫，但 Pixel 4 XL 始終是一部高階旗艦，售價並不便宜，消費者對質量有一定期望。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yyqNR6W_MUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyyqNR6W_MUQ&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=5ceabddb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yyqNR6W_MUQ</a>"},{"pid":"98133bada41b7110daf03cd217a47fbc4a69e7fb","tid":1697552,"uid":109923,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T02:39:02.000Z","msg":"仲廢過屌米部S855機 K20 Pro<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我俾你原生an加返500蚊啦，google信仰都加500，非支那機再加500<br />\nPixel賣屌米K20 Pro嘅價+1500就差唔多啦，大概HKD4000咁上下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ufW1Ogsq83o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FufW1Ogsq83o&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=cc01fa69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ufW1Ogsq83o</a>"},{"pid":"dfd2b48e2eb19114507f654b11701cf59de2b512","tid":1697552,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T02:48:34.000Z","msg":"跟iphone 用不銹鋼邊框囉，唔怕重嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5a19e8479be32d56d18ab28eacff058db58be7","tid":1697552,"uid":83,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:00:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pixel 4 XL 的硬件和其他旗艦有一段距離，例如抗刮測試在 Level 6 就已經出現屏幕刮痕，到了 Level 7 更出現明顯刮花。</blockquote><br />\n篇文邊個打架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d14b96f41c73c1c5e86137f706e01ade9baa96c","tid":1697552,"uid":2766,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:08:53.000Z","msg":"pixel都唔值佢個價<br />\n除咗信仰真係唔知咩原因會買"},{"pid":"a6731ea0852e6d8a8481d8fff2228ddd48f4c4eb","tid":1697552,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9e5a19e8479be32d56d18ab28eacff058db58be7","tid":1697552,"uid":83,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:00:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pixel 4 XL 的硬件和其他旗艦有一段距離，例如抗刮測試在 Level 6 就已經出現屏幕刮痕，到了 Level 7 更出現明顯刮花。</blockquote><br />\n篇文邊個打架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:11:01.000Z","msg":"Pixel 4 XL 一拗即斷   四點斷裂情況慘不忍睹<br />\n虎仔 / 馬日山(uniqlo) 2019-11-06 12:21<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4541/214464/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4541%2F214464%2F1%2F&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=757b9250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/